Anatomy of the Stack

ESP (Extended Stack Pointer) -> top
|
Buffer Space -> Vậy khai thác buffer over flow là nói đến "Poor input Sanitation" 
|
EBP (Extended Base Pointer) -> base
|
EIP (Extended Instruction Pointer) / Return Address
